  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the effect of routine FFR-guided complete
      revascularization with PCI compared to conservative management in patients with concomitant
      coronary artery disease who are undergoing TAVI.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
